              gzip 1.2.4 (18 Aug 93) + bzip2 patch(by Iida-san)

     [UN|X]  FreeBSD 2.2.7-RELEASE, Linux 2.0.30, Solaris2.6, HP-UX 9.07
              LHa for UNIX  V 1.14c
              UnZip 5.32 of 3 November 1997
              Zip 2.2 (November 3rd 1997)
