3.14 File folder
================

File Folder gives the view for local file system.  The one File Folder
corresponds to the one directory.

   Format:

     'file:' PATH-OF-THE-DIRECTORY

   Example:

     file:~/work     -> ~/work
     file:/etc       -> /etc


