'q'
     Exit current folder.  ('wl-summary-exit')

'j'
     Jump cursor to the currently displayed message's window.
     ('wl-summary-jump-to-current-message')

'J'
     Jump cursor to the other message.  ('wl-summary-jump-to-msg')

